6. UPDATED README (REPLACE YOUR CURRENT ONE IF YOU WANT)
# 1STEP · MEOAI — Automation Engine (Expo + Expo Router)

1STEP is a next-generation mobile AI system designed to perform instant actions, automate complex workflows, and streamline everyday tasks with a single step.

This repo contains the **1STEP / MEOAI MVP app**, built with **Expo** and **Expo Router**, ready to be extended into a full automation platform for life, brand, and business.

---

## Tech Stack

- Expo (React Native)
- Expo Router (tabs navigation)
- React
- React Native
- Simple MEOAI engine placeholder (lib/ai.js)

---

## Screens

- **Dashboard (Home)** — Command center overview
- **Actions** — AI command input & response (MEOAI demo)
- **Tasks** — Example automations and routines
- **Settings** — Owner / brand info and future integrations

---

## Getting Started (Local Dev)

Clone the repo:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/HSW365/1step-MEOai.git
cd 1step-MEOai


Install dependencies:

npm install


Run the app:

npx expo start
